item.description:
@ottkid2 wrote:

this happens on every 500+ server i try for some reason im getting pissed

[quote=“Loveandpower, post:2, topic:428247”]from the error it’s giving it’s stating there is no constructor after a quick google search I found this

blog.bdoughan.com

JAXB and Immutable Objects

I was recently sent a blog post:  JAXB and immutable objects , by Aniket Shaligram.  In this post the author addresses the issue by adding ...

it explains about this type of stuff…sort of…or more of a subsitute I don’t know :S I have seen a couple of problems related to yours before though. (related to npcdrops I believe though…) so just trying to help get this a solved solution for everybody[/quote]
